if enrich_only:
    return await enrich_company_board(...)
try:
    return await scrape_company_board(...)
except FetchCancelled:
    raise
except Exception as exc:
    ...
```

Removed unused `_ERROR_RE`. All 23 scrape/fetch tests still pass.

